Package: raveR
Title: R Scripts to Deep House Music
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Transform R scripts into listenable deep house music. RaveR provides
    waveform synthesis, pre-rendered buffer architecture for GC-pause-free
    playback, and audio export capabilities.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
